					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I don't know why she thinks there's anyone on this entire planet who'd be able to forget something like that.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"这个世界上存在着会忘记这种事情的人吗？",
